title: BIG FACTS feat. DOMANI / K CAMP
itunes:title: BIG FACTS feat. DOMANI / K CAMP
description:
In a 2 segment episode, the BIG FACTS posse has a conversation with T.I.'s son DOMANI in segment 1.

Domani talks about life when you are born in stardom, staying away from controversy and his music career.

In segment 2, K CAMP gives an update on what's been going on with him and what's to come.
